        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Discussion:\n\n-Literal: \" We found that Myo9a localizes at synapses and directly interacts with the AMPAR subunit GluA2.\". Experimental description: Results section: \"Myo9a Localizes to the PSD and Directly\nInteracts with the AMPAR Subunit GluA2\"\n\nLiteral: \"We used anti-GluA2/3 antibodies to immunopurify AMPARs and their interacting proteins from primary cultures of rat hippocampal neurons (Figure 1A).\"" ;
